The parade of souls. Spiralized into mesher,
void-like movements, the master portal defines
its parameters through vital connections between
the orbs. All that it is, isn't, and all the it 
was, is. The parade constructs an intense pull
under and over its organized patterns and gravitation.
What does it lead to?
